SUMMARY:Aki Kumar Birthday Bash
DESCRIPTION:San Jose’s “King of the Bollywood Blues”\nBlues harmonica ace Aki Kumar – San Jose’s “King of The Bollywood Blues” celebrates his birthday in Santa Rosa with a big blues bash! Following their successful debut at this venue in 2024\, Kumar’s band makes its second\, eagerly anticipated appearance at The California Theater. His award-winning band includes rhythm section heavies June Core and Randy Bermudes and the amazing Rome Yamilov on guitar. \nBUY TIX IN ADVANCE AND SAVE!\nTickets $25 in advance\, $32 at the door\nDoors open 6:30 pm. Show starts 7:30pm
