SUMMARY:Sunday Sessions with "Fire Up!"
DESCRIPTION:Griffo is excited to welcome Fire Up!\, a Bay Area Tribute to the Garcia Saunders Songbook. This rotating cast of players will have you transported with the first tune. Bodega Market Deli will be serving up food all day while the Griffo crew serves up delicious cocktails from our ever rotating menu! Don’t miss this homage to an era of music that never goes out of style!\nSee you Sundays! \nWho’s Playing: Fire Up!\nWho’s Cooking: Bodega Market Deli\nWhen: Sunday\, March 15th – Doors @ 1 pm\nWhere: Griffo Distillery\nPlease RSVP for this FREE\, All Ages Event. Space is Limited. \nAbout the Band:\nFire up! Is a tribute band interpreting the Jerry Garcia “Legion of Mary” era. Fire Up! is branded as “Songs from the Garcia – Saunders songbook.”\nFor note\, Fire Up! is a name of a Garcia Saunders studio album\, https://open.spotify.com/album/2b85gbWiMbAg3cvSUTMIBp\nOur project is funky\, bluesy\, Jamy\, RnB\, and Jazzy with an emphasis on the Hammond organ. One might say “Ballroom brawling\, baby making music” modeled after the 1972 – 1975 Legion of Mary era. It is different than what you hear from other JGB bands who focus on more of the 80’s and 90’s gospel Jerry era.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/sunday-sessions-with-fire-up/
LOCATION:Griffo Distillery\, 1320 Scott Street\, Petaluma\, CA
GEO:38.2705;-122.664
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Griffo Distillery 1320 Scott Street Petaluma CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=1320 Scott Street:geo:-122.664,38.2705
END:VEVENT
